OL,3,CPark home owners forced out of beloved
OL,4,Ccommunity as landlord sells site
OL,6,FPeople living on a caravan park near
OL,7,FWeston-super-Mare have been told they
OL,8,Fmust move out and leave their much-
OL,9,Floved community behind.
OL,11,FThe former landowner of Sun Valley
OL,12,FCaravan Park, in Kewstoke, has sold
OL,13,Fthe site and a new company has served
OL,14,Fnotice.
OL,16,FWhile it is on the outskirts of the
OL,17,Fpopular tourist town of Weston-super-
OL,18,FMare, Sun Valley Caravan Park is also
OL,19,Fa permanent home to many.
