OL,3,CPark home owners forced out of beloved
OL,4,Ccommunity as landlord sells site
OL,6,FMany of those living on the site
OL,7,Fassumed they would be able to spend
OL,8,Fthe rest of their lives there.
OL,10,FSam Hole is a care worker who has
OL,11,Flived on the site for eight years. Her
OL,12,Ftwo-bed, ensuite caravan cost her
OL,13,F#60,000.
OL,15,FShe has now been given 60 days to
OL,16,Fleave by the firm which owns the land
OL,17,F- meaning she must leave by September.
