OL,3,CPark home owners forced out of beloved
OL,4,Ccommunity as landlord sells site
OL,6,F"I bought it off of the lady who owned
OL,7,Fthe site originally. It was my forever
OL,8,Fhome. I handed the money over and
OL,9,Fthat's what I thought," she said.
OL,11,FSam's friend Christine Ogston also
OL,12,Flives on the site.
OL,14,FChristine works in a hospice and her
OL,15,Fhusband is recovering from cancer.
OL,16,FThey put their life savings into their
OL,17,Fstatic park home 15 years ago.
