OL,4,Ccommunity as landlord sells site
OL,6,FWhile they have managed to find
OL,7,Fsomewhere else to live, signing a
OL,8,Fcontract to move into a council flat,
OL,9,Fthey say it is not the retirement they
OL,10,Fhad hoped for by the beach.
OL,12,F"We just signed the contacts for a
OL,13,Fflat, three storeys up. It's
OL,14,Fcompletely different to this. We don't
OL,15,Fwant to move - it's heartbreaking."
OL,17,FStruggling to speak through tears,
OL,18,FChristine told ITV News: "I'm 76, my
OL,19,Fhusband is 77 and he hasn't got very
OL,20,Fgood health. We thought we'd be here
OL,21,Ffor the rest of our lives really.
