OL,6,F"We've got so many friends here."
OL,8,FDespite requests, the landowner, LT
OL,9,FManagement did not respond to ITV
OL,10,FNews's request for an interview.
OL,12,FA North Somerset Council spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We're aware of the situation at
OL,14,FSun Valley Caravan Park in Kewstoke
OL,15,Fand the council's Homeless Prevention
OL,16,Fteam have sent letters to all
OL,17,Fresidents and visited the park with
OL,18,Fhousing officers and an adult social
OL,19,Fcare worker to ensure residents get
OL,20,Fthe right help and support.
